StringLiteralExpr.value: You should provide a time series.
dim must be a scalar or a vector.
tau must be a scalar or a vector.
logr must be a scalar or a vector.
logr must be a positive scalar or vector
w must be either a scalar or a vector.
svd must be either a scalar or a vector.
q must be either a scalar or a vector.
Only one of dim, tau, p, w, svd, or q should be vector.
